text: Input/Output Data The input/output data is the type of data that an agent expects to receive and delivers. The agent expects AMQP UDRs of type: Received Publish RequestCycle Subscribe and it can deliver AMQP UDRs of type: Received Error RequestCycle SubscribeOK See AMQP UDRs for further information. MIM The AMQP agent does not have any agent-specific MIM paraders. For information about the MIM and a list of the general MIM parameters, see MIM .
